# Package Manager Preference: Use pnpm

This project uses pnpm as the preferred package manager and task runner.

-   Instead of `npm install`, use `pnpm install`.
-   Instead of `npm install <package>` or `npm i <package>`, use `pnpm add <package>`.
-   Instead of `npm uninstall <package>`, use `pnpm remove <package>`.
-   Instead of `npx <command>`, use `pnpx <command>`.
